---
Source:
  - Title: The Collected Songs of Cold Mountain
    Publisher: Copper Canyon Press
    Translator: Red Pine
    ISBN: 1556591403
Author: Han Shan
Page: 247
---
The quick-thinking people I meet
look and know the meaning
they don't bother with scriptures
they go straight to the buddha stage
their hearts don't chase connections
theur minds don't form delusions
once the heart and mind are still
all work is finished inside and out
